You can share a trended dashboard just as you can with any CRM Analytics dashboard. To share the trending dashboard, use CRM Analytics or Templated Apps and Trend Report Data in CRM Analytics.

Share a trending dashboard by:

Posting an image to a feed
Downloading and sharing an image
Embedding your trending CRM Analytics dashboard
Sharing the underlying snapshots dataset by saving it to a CRM Analytics app

Important:
Sharing the trending CRM Analytics dashboard or underlying dataset could expose data to users who normally wouldn't have access.
title: Sharing Trending Dashboards in Salesforce Analytics
